Package: r4clinstats
Title: Learn R for Clinical Statistics, Interactively
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R:
    person("A. P. S.", "Munro", email = "apsmunro@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A swirl-style, learn-by-doing course that teaches clinicians and
    clinical researchers to wrangle, tidy, visualise and analyse clinical data
    in R. Lessons are interactive 'learnr' tutorials graded by 'gradethis',
    built on the tidyverse and real-feeling synthetic clinical datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
